&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;The ACLU seeks a &lt;strong&gt;Legal&lt;/strong&gt; Intern in the &lt;strong&gt;Human Rights Program&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;of the ACLU’s National office in &lt;strong&gt;New York City.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;This is a Hybrid, part-time position for course credit only.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
