&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills, both verbal and writing&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail, excellent organization and time-management skills&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Microsoft Office Suite&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The initiative to see projects through to completion&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated commitment to public interest law, civil liberties,&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;racial justice&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to conduct complex legal analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Kindness, generosity, and humility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
