&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;The ACLU seeks an&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Undergraduate Artist &amp;amp; Influencer Engagement &lt;/strong&gt;Intern on the &lt;strong&gt;A&amp;amp;E&amp;nbsp;team in the Communications Department&lt;/strong&gt; of the ACLU’s National office&lt;strong&gt;. This is a full-time or part-time position&lt;/strong&gt; that can be&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;remote&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;or&amp;nbsp;based in our&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;NY Office&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
