&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be committed to advancing the mission of

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;The ACLU seeks an &lt;strong&gt;Undergraduate &lt;/strong&gt;Intern in the &lt;strong&gt;Communications and Marketing Department&lt;/strong&gt; of the ACLU’s National office&lt;strong&gt;. This is a part-time position&lt;/strong&gt; that can be based in&lt;strong&gt; Washington D.C., New York or remote.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
