&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The ACLU&#39;s&amp;nbsp;Nationwide Portfolio Strategy and Prospect Development (NPSPD)&amp;nbsp;team&amp;nbsp;focuses on&amp;nbsp;a&amp;nbsp;number of&amp;nbsp;prospect development efforts&amp;nbsp;to support&amp;nbsp;major gifts&amp;nbsp;fundraising, including prospect identification, prospect research, and portfolio management.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
